title: Da Wei Bei Ken Zhi Daomei Tegong Xiong
synopsis: With the over-exploitation of natural resources by humans, the Arctic environment is completely destroyed, leaving only the last polar bear to survive. The human girl Jessica adopted this polar bear and named him Bacon. Jessica is an excellent agent of the Ministry of Security. Although Bacon also dreamed of being an agent, he was clumsy and always getting into trouble, he could only do cleaning work in the security department. The mysterious organization of polar bears that suddenly appeared and planted bombs all over the world, claiming to retaliate against mankind. In order to remove the bomb threat, the highest decision-making body of mankind, the Global Alliance, sent security agents to sneak into the polar bear base, but unexpectedly there was a human detector in the base, which made the infiltration fail. The Global Alliance had to train Bacon as an agent and send it to the polar bear base. Jessica secretly accompanied him, worried about Becken's safety. Bacon and Jessica have encountered many obstacles in the polar bear base, but they are always able to make mistakes. Although they finally resolved the bomb crisis, Bacon was caught. The leader of the mysterious organization revealed the amazing truth to Beacon... and the Global Alliance is preparing to abandon Beacon and launch a full-scale attack on the polar bear organization...(translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 大卫贝肯之倒霉特工熊

title: Zhongkui Chuanqi Zhi Sui Han Sanyou
synopsis: Zhong Kui, the legendary No. 1 scholar in the Tang Dynasty, was outstanding in talent and martial arts, but because of his ugly appearance, he was removed from the title of No. 1 by the emperor. Zhong Kui was ashamed and angrily killed in the hall. Because of his uprightness, he was named Emperor Fumo by the Jade Emperor. Because he reported that he was guilty of corruption in the underworld, he was hated by the king and wanted to get rid of Zhong Kui, so he tampered with the life and death book of Zhong Kui's friend Liu Kai to force Zhong Kui to submit. Zhong Kui, Liu Kai, and Ouyang Yiqing cooperated with each other to start a just battle between the underworld and the sun. (translated from douban)

title: Dou Fu Chuan
synopsis: During the reign of Emperor Wu of the Western Han Dynasty, Huainan King Liu An advocated the immortal method and collected beans to practice elixir. The elixir was not refined, but the beans were transformed into human form and became a "bean tribe." The protagonist Dou Fu is as obsessed with immortality as Liu An, but he hasn't attained immortality after years of hard practice. Douxiang, a childhood sweetheart and like-minded friends, doubted Xianshu and persuaded him to give up, but Doufu persisted. 　　A chance coincidence, Doufu ran into a neurotic Nervous Dou in the neuropathy. Under the guidance of Nervous Dou, Doufu’s fairy skills were advancing by leaps and bounds, and the conspiracy behind Xiu Xian began to surface... (translated from douban)

title: Dan Jihua
synopsis: The "Egg Project" is a plan to protect small animals. The carrot rabbit and the potato (the potato is a blue turtle) are members of the Earth Animal Protection Organization. Carrot Rabbit is a fashionable doctor, while Potato Turtle is an old-fashioned mechanic. In order to protect the dinosaur eggs, they came to a mysterious planet in the depths of the universe-Dragon Egg Planet. On the planet Dragon Egg, there are egg-eaters that live on eggs. Under the threat of egg-eaters, the dinosaur eggs here are on the verge of extinction. To protect the fear of these precious species (translated from baidu)

title: Dan Jihua Zhi Shi Dan Shou Jiazu
synopsis: Carrot Bunny and Potato successfully saved many dragon eggs on Dragon Egg planet. The egg-eater did not eat an egg vigorously. At this time, Dali's grandfather and sister Xiaomei came. The old-fashioned grandfather is a big wise and foolish egg-eater, while the petite and swift little Mei is a crazy cute...(translated from baidu)

title: Dan Jihua Zhi Huanle Xingqiu
synopsis: In order to protect the dinosaur eggs, they came to a mysterious planet in the depths of the universe-Dragon Egg Planet. On the planet Dragon Egg, there are egg-eaters that live on eggs. Under the threat of egg-eaters, the dinosaur eggs here are on the verge of extinction. In order to protect the dinosaur eggs of these precious species, carrot rabbits and potatoes must hatch the baby dinosaurs before the egg-eaters. So the carrot rabbit and the potato and the egg-eater started a battle for eggs. (translated from douban)

title: Dan Jihua Zhi Long Shou Xingqiu
synopsis: No synopsis information has been added to this title. Help improve our database by adding a synopsis here.

title: Luobo Tu Ai Faxian
synopsis: Carrot rabbits and potatoes rushed to the world on the train Discovery to help animal friends solve problems one by one. (translated from baidu)

title: Dan Jihua Da Dianying
synopsis: The "Egg Project" movie is about: Carrot Bunny and Potato Turtle, who have been protecting Dragon Egg on Dragon Egg Planet, suddenly receive a mysterious task. This task requires the help of Han Bagui who has been immersed in researching Zhenlong Eggs, but Han Bagui's home was ransacked once by a mysterious figure who had taken the lead, and no one was there. This made Tudou suspect the huge conspiracy, and then the news came that Hanbagui and the residents of Dragondan Planet-Dali and Xiaomei were kidnapped. In order to save Hanbagui and even more seeking the truth, Tudou and Carrot Rabbit embark on a thrilling but touching adventure. Who kidnapped the Han Bagui, and what caused the potato and the carrot rabbit to become dangerous. Behind the conspiracy was another conspiracy. The potato and the carrot rabbit went through hardships during the adventure. Explore the truth in the dark vortex. " (translated from iqiyi)

title: Dan Jihua Shehui Jiaowang Ertong Xilie Gushi
synopsis: The series of social conflicts that children may encounter in life are used as original materials and presented in the form of animation, such as slapstick, antagonism, pride, bullying and other behaviors. The "Egg Project Social Interaction Children's Story Series" includes four aspects: behavioral norms, friendly relationship with others, caring and respecting them, self-esteem and self-confidence, and autonomy. It contains social etiquette, social norms, etc., and aims to improve children's social interaction. Ability to cultivate a good sense of social communication skills. (translated from iqiyi)

details.Japanese: 蛋计划社会交往儿童系列故事

title: Dan Jihua Anquan Ertong Xilie Gushi
synopsis: A series of potential safety hazards that children may encounter in life are used as original materials and presented in the form of animation, such as falling, electric shock, abduction, and drowning. The "Egg Project" safe children series of stories covers five aspects of health and safety, home safety, activity safety, traffic safety, and natural disaster safety. It includes safety education, physical exercise, hygiene habits, etc., and aims to improve children’s crisis management Ability to cultivate the awareness of good living habits. (translated from iqiyi)

details.Japanese: 蛋计划安全儿童系列故事

title: Dan Jihua Luoji Siwei Ertong Xilie Gushi
synopsis: A series of logical problems that children may encounter in life are used as original materials and presented in the form of animation, such as mathematics, puzzles, guessing, and solving crimes. The "Egg Project" series of logical thinking children's stories includes five aspects: puzzle games, mathematical world, detective solving, comparative observation, and general creation. It includes content such as judgment and reasoning, mathematics in life, and aims to improve children's logical thinking. Ability, cultivate rational thinking consciousness, and lay the foundation for the convergence of young children.(translated from iqiyi)

details.Japanese: 蛋计划逻辑思维儿童系列故事

title: Dan Jihua Tansuo Faxian Ertong Xilie Gushi
synopsis: Taking a series of explorations and discovering natural scenes that children may encounter in life as original materials, they are presented in the form of animation, such as the change of seasons, the reproduction of animals and other natural phenomena. The "Egg Project Discovery Series of Children's Stories" covers five aspects of the wonderful ocean, animal kingdom, dinosaur world, plant world, and world human landscape, aiming to enhance children's ability to explore and discover, and cultivate children's keen observation and logical rationality Consciousness of thinking. (translated from iqiyi)

details.Japanese: 蛋计划探索发现儿童系列故事

title: Dan Jihua Ertong Xilie Gushi
synopsis: Duobao is a cheerful and sunny child. He is in the stage of learning in many aspects as he is in kindergarten. In the process of continuous learning and growth, Duobao has absorbed knowledge in the fields of health, etiquette, puzzles, safety, habits, and psychology. In every field, Duobao will encounter or see common but often overlooked problems that occur around him, small knowledge, great principles, and Dubao strives to lay a good foundation for his healthy growth. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Wo De Baba Shi Guowang
synopsis: Far away, there is a magical kingdom of Noah, the kingdom of Noah. The king of Noah’s kingdom is often unable to accompany his little daughter, Princess Lily, due to his busy schedule. Princess Lily, who lacks the company of her parents, left the magic school and ran to magic alone. In the market, Lily, who is quirky in nature, curious and playful, followed the magic pet to the magic pet kingdom under the rule of Queen Aps. Queen Aps decided to discipline this naughty and willful little princess. Princess Lily became a magic castle. The pet workers were also made things difficult for by the Queen. At the same time, two villains from another kingdom, Gluru and Fasha, also sneaked into the queen's palace to steal magic pets. The king, who was busy dealing with state affairs, was told by the head of the magic school Gandalf that his daughter, Princess Lily, was missing. The king was anxious and left the government and the princess’s few friends embarked on a journey to find and rescue the princess... (translated from douban)

title: Kyousougiga PV
synopsis: The original Kyousougiga PV featuring completely original content that aired before the 2011 25-minute ONA.

title: Ying Huo Qibing
synopsis: Deng Deng (Shan Xin dubbing) is a firefly that can emit a shining light. It is regarded as an idol by the likes. Deng Deng is very proud of this. One day, an alien named Aurora (voiced by Guo Sheng) came to Deng Deng. From then on, Deng Deng was no longer the brightest existence, which made Deng Deng feel extremely lost. At this juncture, the evil and greedy unicorn (voiced by Deng Weifeng) tricked the lantern into a lisp, causing it to fall into the trap of the Great Wolf King (voiced by Baomu Zhongyang) and be jailed. 　　 Knowing the unfortunate situation of Deng Deng, Aurora stepped forward and led Deng Deng's friends Agui (voiced by Yao Lei) and Xiao Huxian (voiced by Li Shanshan) on a journey of understanding and saving Deng Deng. Can they defeat the Great Wolf King and his minions, and rescue the Lantern smoothly and safely? (translated from bouban)

title: Ying Huo Qibing 2: Xiao Chong Bu Hao Re
synopsis: The firefly "Deng Deng" and its insect buddies formed a special action team called "Fireflies" to help insect friends in distress. At the same time, an alien came to a spacecraft, and this spacecraft contained great danger. (translated from douban)

title: Shi Xian
synopsis: More than a hundred years ago, the human world was destroyed by the time-string power from the universe. Mutation, killing, and war ensued. In order to avoid being chased by monsters, human beings gathered in the last pure land of Simai, living like a beast. One rainy night, the leader of the expeditionary army suddenly rebelled against Simak, and that night, the expeditionary army was mass murdered. Ye Yuze, who was from the expedition team and now the captain of the garrison, remembered what Kebei Dao said to him before he left, and there seemed to be some conspiracy hidden in Simak City. At the same time that Ye Yuze was investigating, high-level officials convened a meeting to carve up the remaining troops of the expeditionary force. President Du Lixun ordered that all people related to Kebei Island be killed. This was the beginning of a larger-scale suppression of Ximai City. Ye Yuze broke through the barriers of the soldiers, rescued the daughter of Kebei Island, Twilight, and escaped from Simai City. However, during the conversation, Ye Yuze felt more and more that things were far from being as simple as he thought, and that even greater conspiracies had slowly attacked the entire human world...(translated from iqiyi)

title: Yoi Kono Tanoshii Christmas
synopsis: A direct-to-video collection of nine Christmas-themed music videos.

details.Japanese: よいこのたのしいクリスマス

title: Da Xiang Lin Wang Zhi Yi Pao Chengming
synopsis: Lin Wang (voiced by Song Xiaoyu) is a lively and cute baby elephant living happily in the jungle on the border between Yunnan and Myanmar. Lin Wang's good friend is a Chinese boy named Wang Zai (voiced by Li Yao). The friendship between one person and one elephant is very deep. Lin Wang, who likes to be naughty and mischievous, often causes a lot of trouble and jokes, but it is still loved by animals. The good times didn’t last long. The war started. The Japanese’s iron hooves broke through the tranquility of the jungle. Both Lin Wang and Wang’s cubs were captured by the Japanese and became coolies. In the army, Lin Wang knew many people from different places who had the same The elephants who suffered tragically, they decided to join forces to fight back. The arrival of the Chinese Expeditionary Army ended the miserable lives of Lin Wang and Wang's cubs. Lin Wang joined the army as a war elephant.(translated from douban)

title: Wan Ou Qibing
synopsis: Once, dolls were the best playmates for children, and they spent a carefree time with each other. However, this time is short. Since the advent of ipad games, children have been addicted to it and can no longer be interested in dolls. Seeing the little master lost in the virtual digital world, the dolls decided to join hands and dive into the crisis-ridden game world to save their little master. In this way, the brave, kind, upright and tough Mini Tiger (voiced by Yan Lizhen), the toothless boy (voiced by Li Ye) who is frail and sickly but has a super IQ (voiced by Li Ye) and the steady, wise and quiet Tin Man (voiced by Wang Heng) joined hands on the journey In addition to the countless crises and troubles waiting for them along the way, there is also a crisis of trust within the dolls. (translated from douban)

title: Xiha Ying Xiong
synopsis: The hip-hop bear is only to rescue the “hip-hop” bear cubs abducted by hunters. The reckless bear dad “Dashan” broke into the lively human town during the festival; when the mountain was about to be captured, he was caught by a mysterious agent. The dog "Hunt" was saved. At this time, hip-hop has fallen into the magic cave of the animal trading group, and was dressed as a panda by bad guys, and his value has soared. In order to save his son, Dashan and Hunt formed an animal agent partner and launched a secret operation to sneak into the magic cave; the truck full of animals is about to set off, and rescue is urgent! But the mysterious Hunter took Dashan to another place...What secret does Agent Dog Hunter hide? Can the reckless Dashan survive the ordeal and rescue his dependent son?(translated from douban)

title: Da Xiongmao Chuanqi
synopsis: The legendary "iron-eater" broke into the village, Xiaoqing and Guoshan brothers and sisters went deep into the mountains to look for the "iron-eater", but accidentally discovered that the so-called "iron-eater" was a pair of mother and child giant pandas fleeing for food. 　　 At the same time, the ferocious and cunning old snow leopard "one-eyed", the fierce and cruel red wolf, and the criminals seeking huge profits have all focused on the mother and child giant pandas, which is even worse for the endangered pandas. 　　 To help the fleeing mother and child giant pandas, Xiaoqing and Guoshan went deep into the mountain to deliver food for the mother and child giant pandas. The brothers and sisters not only have to face the dangerous natural environment, but also always beware of the ferocious beasts. But after they completed the task of delivering food to the mother and child of the giant panda and won the trust of the mother and child, they discovered that the mother and child were mysteriously missing. . The brothers and sisters looked for the mother and child of the giant panda based on various clues, but at this time the mother and child of the giant panda were already hungry and cold. Not only were they chased by criminals and had nowhere to hide, they were also ambushed by a red wolf, and the more vicious one-eyed leopard followed. Waiting for the opportunity. In order to protect the baby panda, the mother panda stepped forward resolutely and fought against criminals, red wolves and one-eyed leopards in Devil Ridge... 　　 Xiaoqing and Guoshan finally found the mother and child of the giant panda. With the help of Daddy Caowa, Dr. Leng and everyone, the giant panda was not only rescued successfully, but also accumulated valuable experience for scientific rescue of the giant panda.(translated from douban)

title: Muye Chuanqi
synopsis: Based on the well-known legend in China, "The Romance of the Gods", it tells the story of the young emperor Wu Wang Jifa's growth in adversity. It is the story of Wu Wang Jifa from scratch, through hardships, and finally ascended to the top of life. 　　 In the last years of the Shang Dynasty, the king had no way, natural and man-made disasters followed one after another, and demons harmed the world. In order to obtain the legendary Dragon Sword, the Nine-Tailed Fox set off a bloody storm in the Longyin town on the border of Xiqi. Ji Fa, the second son of Xibo Hou Jichang, the lord of Xiqi, eliminated harm to the people, obtained the Dragonyin Sword, and cut off a tail of the nine-tailed fox. 　　 The nine-tailed fox, in order to avenge the tail-breaking, possessed his concubine Su Daji, entered the palace to confuse King Zhou, framed the family of Xibohou, and imprisoned Xibohou in Yili City for seven years. With the help of Nezha, Lei Zhenzi and others, Ji Fa rescued his father. 　　 King Zhou became more and more cruel, causing anger and resentment. The princes from all walks of life united and took Jifa as their leader to start a decisive battle with King Zhou's army in Muye City. Under the guidance of Jiang Ziya, Ji Fa comprehended the realm of "non-self", exerted the power of the Dragon Yin Sword to its extreme, broke through the immortal formation, and led troops into Chaoge City. King Zhou set himself on fire, and the nine-tailed fox punished him, and the Zhou Dynasty was established. (translated from douban)

title: Xin Ba Da Yu Meirenyu Gongzhu
synopsis: The film tells that there is an "ideal island" rich in gold in the Atlantic Ocean. It is Sinbad's dream to find it. But as a small shipyard worker, Sinbad was not even qualified to go to sea, until the boss of the casino helped him win three "pirates", Sinbad finally got a ship and these three servants. In this way, no luck Sinbad, the mermaid princess Shirley, foodie Kaka and cute cat Dom formed a sailing team and set off for the "ideal island". They encountered storms and huge waves, as well as the kingdom’s guard warships, as well as terrifying underwater monsters... finally reached the "ideal island", but there is a more terrifying secret hidden on the "ideal island"-the reborn sea god Poseidon Waiting for the arrival of the new body. (translated from douban)

title: Shuishen Wa
synopsis: The Water God Empress is guarding the canal, but the Dragon King of Bitter Sea has been coveting the treasure map in her hand for a long time. Finally one day the Dragon King of Bitter Sea and the Empress of the Water God are facing each other. This coincides with the birth of the child of the God of Water. In the shell. Shui Bao was adopted by a kind bachelor. Before he died, his adoptive father told Shui Bao his life experience. After he grew up, Shui Bao embarked on a journey with his friends, and finally avenged his mother and guarded the canal. (translated from douban)

title: Zhen Jia Senlin Wang
synopsis: This film is a new edition of the classic story "Fake Fox and Tiger". It mainly tells that Fox, the mixed-haired fox, in order to save his son Xiaofu, faked the tiger king Locke, and fought with the tortoise family, and finally succeeded in smashing the tortoise and its cold-blooded family to rule the forest Although he did not become the real king of the forest, he won the trust of the tiger king and became the brains of the forest king. (translated from douban)

title: Tai Yi Xian Mo Lu Zhi Ling Fei Ji III
synopsis: No synopsis information has been added to this title. Help improve our database by adding a synopsis here.

details.Synonyms: Tai Yi Xian Mo Lu Zhi Ling Fei Ji 3rd Season

title: Ai Ni Zhidao Shijie Jintou
synopsis: Wang Ba Di is the designer of the photo studio (actually it is a P picture). He is withdrawn in appearance but sullen on the inside and is keen to spit out his stomach. He has an amazing special skill: Anything with texture, he can see the pattern and associate it, and come up with a scene and a story. When he broke up with Mu Bei, he was treated for his emotional injury at his brother Wang Xiaolan's house. The frustrated and sloppy traveled in his dreams all day long, contemplating the illusion of happiness with his girlfriend Mu Bei. Under the stimulation of Wang Xiaolan, he determined to contact Mubei again. Will he wait until Mubei's arrival, worrying, what kind of mysterious identity will Wang Xiaolan, who is in the shadows, have? (translated from douban)

title: Jue Ji 2: Lengxue Kuang Yan
synopsis: In order to fulfill the last wish of the first six-degree king Syluel, Silver Dust, Qi Ling, Tianshu Youhua and others decided to go together to rescue the former king Gilgamesh who was sealed by the silver priest. After overcoming numerous obstacles and rushing to the place of imprisonment, unfortunately, he encountered the strongest assassin lineup sent by the silver priest: Nether, Terea, and Sila. A head-on confrontation is inevitable, and the darkest secret of the entire Yaslan Empire is also Will gradually surface. (translated from douban)

title: Mama Mi Ya
synopsis: The big little yellow duck movie "Mommy Duck" tells the story of the geese migrating south, the "best pilot" Dapeng rebelliously loves to make trouble, and accidentally collides with his girlfriend Jingjing while flirting with a group of rushing people. Little duck. The disobedient Dapeng decided to fly solo, and had no choice but to form a "temporary father and son stall" with the two ducklings who were alone, and embarked on an oolong journey of finding relatives and moving south. 　　 They experienced a series of thrilling, exciting and interesting adventures. Paddling across the magnificent terraces, climbing over the cold mountains, and encountering their hens and their wives to take care of the roosters, the pigs on the Spring Festival transport truck, and the half-bottled squirrels with Chinese medicine skills. On the way, we must always resist the evil cats who want to eat them, and almost become "roast duck on the plate". The fate of Dapeng and Taotao brothers and sisters are closely related, and the aloof Dapeng has gradually learned responsibility and patience. Finally, the newly renewed Dapeng was forgiven by his girlfriend Jingjing and formed a loving family with the two little ducks.(translated from douban)

title: Xiao Wukong
synopsis: Da Sen was originally a golden monkey in the zoo. He dreamed that one day he could become the Monkey King. Omori and the administrator Guan Guan have a deep friendship. One day, a mysterious monster kidnapped Guan Guan and went to New York. The reason behind this is actually closely related to that of Sun Wukong's slaying of demons thousands of years ago. Omori rushed to New York to rescue Guan Guan and found that the evil force controlling Guan Guan was Sun Wukong’s defeated opponent-Bull Demon King. How to defeat the extremely powerful Bull Demon King became a difficult problem for Omori, Master Ba Jie, and police officer Amo. A very difficult test awaits Omori. Will Omori succeed? (translated from douban)

title: Mao Yu Taohuayuan
synopsis: A blanket for a domestic cat, who often stays in a daze on the windowsill, has been living comfortably with his son in a high-rise apartment in the city. One day the blanket and the cloak had to embark on an adventurous journey to find the peach blossom field of the legendary cat. At the same time, the blanket must face an unwillingness to mention a past in the heart. Perhaps this is also an important reason why the blanket is afraid of the outside world and unwilling to leave home... (translated from douban)

title: Jingche Lianmeng
synopsis: With the dream of a policeman, Xiaozhi came to Xinduhui to search for his missing dad Kaka. In the process, he met friends such as the cleaning truck Tuk Tuk, the ambulance Xiaoyun, the engineering truck Art and the fire truck Da Lei, but he was surprised. Involved in a huge conspiracy to destroy the city's traffic, Xiaozhi, with the determination to find his father, and his companions began the journey against the evil forces... (translated from douban)

title: Da Nao Xiyou
synopsis: Toy Sun Wuyuan considers himself the Monkey King, but is ridiculed in the toy world for not being able to take out the golden hoop. By chance, Sun Wuyuan entered the world of Journey to the West alone, and ran into Monkey King who was driven back to Huaguo Mountain. Sun Wuyuan, who wanted the golden hoop, was stalked, and Sun Wukong reluctantly offered the condition: Sun Wuyuan would worship him as a teacher, and give him the golden hoop after he finished his studies. Unexpectedly, the Bull Demon provoke secretly and instigated Wu Yuan to steal the golden hoop and snatch it away. Five Yuan, who hurriedly fled back to the toy world, discovered that the world has been ruled by cattle...(translated from douban)

title: Jinguizi
synopsis: The animated film "The Scarab" tells the story from the adventure journey of a optimistic insect, the scarab. It lives in the insect box of a rare insect research center "artificial jungle" and leads a simple and happy life. Until one day, a dragonfly from outside broke the calmness... Ge Shui described the world outside the worm box to the chafer. The chafer yearned for it, and it decided to break free from the bondage of the worm box. But is the world outside the worm box really as beautiful as the beetles and friends imagined? Does the legendary "Golden Canyon" really exist? In that new and unknown world, what kind of adventure will the scarab and its friends experience? This is the beginning of a thrilling and interesting adventure! (translated from douban)

title: Meishi Da Maoxian Di Yi Ji: Zheng He Hao Qihang
synopsis: This is an adventure story that takes place in the magical world of food. In order to replenish the sacred book of Nuwa, the creator of the food world, "Nuwa Recipe", Sihai (steamed bread), Baoqiang (baozi), Youwanjin (youtiao), Qiaoqiao (noodles), Yukui (sesame cake), Hua A group of lovely Chinese foods such as Xiaolei (Hanajuan) and Doudou (dumplings), and their friend Musashi (a strong sushi samurai), drive their treasure ship-"Steam Box", on a great voyage adventure in the food world. (translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 美食大冒险第一季：蒸盒号起航

title: Meishi Da Maoxian Di Er Ji: Huore Zhi Lu
synopsis: The complete second season of Gourmet Adventure is the second season of domestic 3D original animation "Gourmet Adventure". The second season of Gourmet Adventure combines various Chinese elements with Chinese noodles as the starting point. It is carefully crafted by an excellent animation team to lead the audience to explore the magical world of food and let the audience experience the animation on the tip of the tongue! (translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 美食大冒险第二季：火热之旅

title: Meishi Da Maoxian Di San Ji: Wenming Zhi Lu
synopsis: The steaming box was sucked into the space-time tunnel, and the crew was scattered. They all embarked on a journey of finding partners by appointment. The Shield of Wisdom was stolen, causing the wrath of Athena, the goddess of wisdom; the night evil hunter appeared on the scene, but was caught by the night evil; the clown knight in the painting was magically resurrected and dragged everyone into the world in the painting. The ambitious big clock that attempts to seal time...The tragic pirate gets magical magic water and becomes an invincible flying pirate group. With all kinds of magical and fantasy experiences, and powerful enemies with different powers, how will the partners of Zhenghehao resolve the crisis? Can they meet again?(translated from douban)

details.Japanese: 美食大冒险第三季：文明之旅

title: Meishi Da Maoxian Zhi Yingxiong Hui
synopsis: This is a world of gourmet food. 　　 Legend has it that Nuwa used magical powers to cast a five-flavored stone, giving food taste and soul. The mountains, rivers and lakes here are composed of food: cheese cliff, bread mountain, onion stone forest, chicken soup lake... all kinds of food live in this world, with their own stories and rivers and lakes.
